libcotp
------------------------------------------
C library that generates TOTP and HOTP according to RFC-6238

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.6-1
  libcotp-devel-2.0.1-1bl1
  libcotp2-2.0.1-1bl1
  libgcrypt-devel-1.10.2-1
  libgcrypt20-1.10.2-1
  pkg-config-1.9.5-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.40-1
  cmake-3.23.2-1
  cygport-0.36.4-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  libgcrypt-devel-1.10.2-1
  ninja-1.11.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/paolostivanin/libcotp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/paolostivanin/libcotp/archive/refs/tags/v2.0.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcotp-2.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcotp-2.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcotp-2.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp-2.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp2-2.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp-devel-2.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcotp)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcotp.README
  /usr/share/doc/libcotp/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libcotp/README.md

(libcotp2)
  /usr/bin/cygcotp-2.dll

(libcotp-devel)
  /usr/include/cotp.h
  /usr/lib/libcotp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/cotp.pc

